    <item>
      <title>修改背包格子上限</title>
      <link>http://nai-8.com/2017/04/19/%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E8%83%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%A0%BC%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%90/</link>
      <guid>http://nai-8.com/2017/04/19/%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E8%83%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%A0%BC%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%90/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Apr 2017 11:52:57 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h1 id=&quot;第一部分&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#第一部分&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;第一部分&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;第一部分&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pocket.h中搜索字段:&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight bash&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;t
      
      </description>
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1 id="第一部分"><a href="#第一部分" class="headerlink" title="第一部分"></a>第一部分</h1><p>Pocket.h中搜索字段:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#define	MAX_POCKET	3</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>如下:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#define	MAX_POCKET	3 // This is the maximum ammount of bag-packs players can have, don`t change this unless you know what you`re doing.</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#define	POCKET_SLOT_SIZE_0	6 // This is the ammount of slots in the FIRST bag-pack.</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#define	POCKET_SLOT_SIZE_1_2	24 // This is the ammount of slots in the TWO EXTRA-BAG-PACKS.</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="第二部分"><a href="#第二部分" class="headerlink" title="第二部分"></a>第二部分</h1><p>在这段代码中数字:6、24为我们可以修改的数值。</p>
<p>我将它改为:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#define	MAX_POCKET	3</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#define	POCKET_SLOT_SIZE_0	6</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#define	POCKET_SLOT_SIZE_1_2	90 //确保这个数值为6的倍数,但最好不要超过96.</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
]]></content:encoded>
      
